  Remove unneeded maintainer-needed.

  12 Aug 2013; Patrick McLean <chutzpah@gentoo.org> metadata.xml:
  Set package to maintainer-needed as I no longer use or care about this
  package.

*courier-imap-4.8.0-r1 (27 Jul 2013)

  27 Jul 2013; Pacho Ramos <pacho@gentoo.org> +courier-imap-4.8.0-r1.ebuild,
  +files/courier-authdaemond.service, +files/courier-imapd-ssl.service,
  +files/courier-imapd.service:
  Install unit file #470746

  13 May 2012; <swift@gentoo.org> courier-imap-4.0.6-r3.ebuild,
  courier-imap-4.5.0.ebuild, courier-imap-4.6.0.ebuild,
  courier-imap-4.8.0.ebuild:
  SELinux policy module for courier-imap is provided by selinux-courier

  25 Apr 2012; Justin Lecher <jlec@gentoo.org> courier-imap-4.0.6-r3.ebuild,
  courier-imap-4.5.0.ebuild, courier-imap-4.6.0.ebuild,
  courier-imap-4.8.0.ebuild:
  Drop unnessecary die

  06 Dec 2011; Bernard Cafarelli <voyageur@gentoo.org> metadata.xml:
  Remove myself from maintainers

  18 Apr 2011; Eray Aslan <eras@gentoo.org> courier-imap-4.0.6-r3.ebuild,
  courier-imap-4.5.0.ebuild, courier-imap-4.6.0.ebuild,
  courier-imap-4.8.0.ebuild:
  revert blocker to net-mail/dovecot introduced while changing to new style
  virtual/imapd

  19 Mar 2011; Eray Aslan <eras@gentoo.org> courier-imap-4.0.6-r3.ebuild,
  courier-imap-4.5.0.ebuild, courier-imap-4.6.0.ebuild,
  courier-imap-4.8.0.ebuild:
  remove old style virtual/imapd

  01 Jul 2010; Bernard Cafarelli <voyageur@gentoo.org>
  courier-imap-4.8.0.ebuild:
  Drop nls USE flag, --disable-unicode is no longer supported, bug #326335

*courier-imap-4.8.0 (28 Jun 2010)

  28 Jun 2010; Bernard Cafarelli <voyageur@gentoo.org>
  +courier-imap-4.8.0.ebuild:
  Version bump

  15 Feb 2010; Raúl Porcel <armin76@gentoo.org>
  courier-imap-4.0.6-r3.ebuild, courier-imap-4.5.0.ebuild,
  courier-imap-4.6.0.ebuild:
  sh stable wrt #279475

