  Marking courier-imap-4.5.0 ppc64 for bug 287933

  23 Nov 2009; Bernard Cafarelli <voyageur@gentoo.org>
  -files/gentoo-pop3d-1.7.3-r1.rc, -files/gentoo-pop3d-ssl-1.7.3-r1.rc,
