*courier-imap-4.6.0 (06 Oct 2009)

  06 Oct 2009; Bernard Cafarelli <voyageur@gentoo.org>
  +courier-imap-4.6.0.ebuild, metadata.xml:
  Version bump, with GCC 4.4 support and ebuild cleanups: EAPI2, drop
  vpopmail setup (courier-imap does not support it anymore), only run
  eautoreconf in needed directories, remove CFLAGS workaround for bug #21330
  (works fine now), add USE flag to enable trashquota (bug #173394)

  06 Oct 2009; Bernard Cafarelli <voyageur@gentoo.org> metadata.xml:
  Add myself to maintainers, so I get bugreports on everything I break

  23 Sep 2009; Patrick Lauer <patrick@gentoo.org> courier-imap-3.0.8.ebuild:
  Remove virtual/libc

  28 Jul 2009; Jeremy Olexa <darkside@gentoo.org>
  -courier-imap-4.0.1-r1.ebuild, -courier-imap-4.0.1-r2.ebuild,
  -courier-imap-4.0.1.ebuild, -courier-imap-4.0.4.ebuild:
  Remove vulnerable versions, bug 271685

  11 Jul 2009; Torsten Veller <tove@gentoo.org>
  courier-imap-4.0.6-r2.ebuild, courier-imap-4.0.6-r3.ebuild,
  courier-imap-4.1.2-r1.ebuild, courier-imap-4.1.2-r2.ebuild,
  courier-imap-4.4.1.ebuild, courier-imap-4.4.1-r1.ebuild,
  courier-imap-4.5.0.ebuild:
  README.gz -> README (#272936)

